{"title":"“黄松岭的火灾”（图片）","authors":["苏坚","马寻"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":6,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“黄松岭的火灾”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏坚书  马寻诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二十四）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驻在山下的解放军，还有老百姓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家闻讯，都一齐出动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们看到火势向森林燃烧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便迅速地应用了战略："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"割草的割草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砍树的砍树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挖道的挖道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"木棒、铁铲、扫帚……人多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"武器也真不少。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"果然，火一扑到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被他们一阵英勇的厮杀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在森林的前面把大敌歼灭了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二十五）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"楞场，林务所……都被大火烧成废丘一片。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工友们烧坏了衣裳，又烧伤了脸！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家默默的看着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"话都没有一句。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是啊，他们用甚么话才能说出他们填胸的悲痛？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这浩大的祖国财产；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这几年的劳动的血汗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所长的棍伤剧烈发痛！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他又疲倦不堪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突然在倒地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感到头昏目眩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工友上前把他扶起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老赵紧张地望着他，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼光像说这样的话："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“记信这沉痛的教训，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——你马虎、麻痹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——你办事不和大家合计！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所长握住老赵的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万句话堵上了咽喉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半天，他才缓缓的开了口："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我，我错了……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼泪像泉水，在脸上流！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二十六）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阎怪头被抓到了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送到政府查办！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所长被撤职了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要他检讨错误的根源！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新的黄松岭的林务所，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在新所长赵景林领导下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——开始重建！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（完）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}